of fame the lists business  wall street  health and life sciences  top  power women top  stars of the south blog events travel gift shop business    donagh herlihyavon products donagh herlihy is senior vice president and cio at avon products inc he leads an information technology organization of  it professionals and is responsible for it strategy and operations globally he reports to the chairman and ceo and is a member of the executive committee his team provides the business systems and technology infrastructure supporting avon’s business operations in more than  countries herlihy joined avon in march  from the wrigley company where he also was cio over his  years there donagh also served successively as vice president of human resources and vp of supply chain strategy and planning donagh holds a bs in industrial engineering from dublin institute of technology  trinity college dublin and has completed the executive program at university of michigan’s ross school of business he is a board member of the american red cross westchester ny donagh was born in dublin and raised in wexford he reflects “my irish upbringing left me very comfortable moving around the world living and working in different environments” charlene begley visit profile tom bradley visit profile conrad burke visit profile steve cahillane visit profile joan carroll visit profile liam casey visit profile cheryl cavanaugh visit profile kieran claffey visit profile aodan coburn visit profile thomas w codd visit profile donald f colleran visit profile frank comerford visit profile james and john concannon visit profile deirdre connelly visit profile adele cooper visit profile catherine coughlin visit profile dennis crowley visit profile pamela daley visit profile bill daly visit profile michael e daniels visit profile a james dehayes visit profile michael j dolan visit profile patrick w dolan visit profile john donahoe visit profile craig s donohue visit profile lisa donohue visit profile brendan doug