rs  donagh herlihy view reviews write new review  reviews are you donagh herlihy claim donaghs profile report a problem with this profile email protected donagh herlihy   executive vice president digital  chief information officer bloomin brands inc donagh herlihy is cio  svp it  ecommerce at avon products inc he leads an information technology organization of  it professionals and is responsible for it strategy and operations globally he reports to the ceo and is a member of the executive committee avon it provides the business systems supporting avon’s operations in more than  countries in addition it is responsible for enabling ecommerce for more than  million avon representatives worldwide avon runs the third largest ecommerce platform globally with more than bn in revenue online major initiatives include driving growth through web social and mobile platforms for avon representatives and consumers driving improved service and efficiency through erp and providing data and analytics to enable growth strategies herlihy joined avon in march  from the wrigley company where he also was cio in his  years at wrigley he drove the transformation of wrigley’s business processes enabled by a global implementation of sap in addition to leading it he also served successively as vice president of human resources and vice president of supply chain prior to wrigley he spent six years at gillette ultimately leading information technology at its duracell subsidiary earlier in his career herlihy was based in the uk where he worked in manufacturing business process reengineering and information technology in both the consumer goods and automotive sectors he holds a bachelor of science degree in industrial engineering from dublin institute of technology  trinity college dublin ireland and he has completed the executive program at the university of michigan ross school of business he is a board member of the american red cross new york videos no videos yet tags request information add